Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,隨著叫龍的活動愈趨頻繁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,各地區陸續傳來了不符常理的巨大個體出沒報告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然暫時派NINES處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們本身還有更重要的任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算放任鶴望蘭到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(939.2,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在特殊樣本的適性報告已經出來的此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,再怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有讓她待在那的理由了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1028,980)}13都市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,此言甚是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她和流有汙穢血液的雄式隨意接觸下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1094.667,980g )}Stamens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對是不智之舉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果把她調回來 那又得配置新的雄式了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1406.667,980)}Stamens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1230.5,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想和那丫頭搭檔的操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,數都數不完
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,夢魘...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是夢魘啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋了才會想和那傢伙搭檔...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,會被殺死的....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,連動都沒動過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺太浪費了 我來幫他解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,自從回來後一直都那副模樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你和Zero Two搭檔時發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你問 發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那女人...居然想將我吸食殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,血液 肉體 靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始都很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 操縱到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 要置我於死地般...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,滿...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,當時還帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她當時在笑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,滿!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再和她搭檔一次 一定會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定也會面臨同樣下場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你以為自己是獨一無二的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再怎麼愚蠢也該有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣 滿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你先好好休養吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我來我來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,輕鬆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是想和她搭檔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1006.667,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對於她的事 我無論如何都信任不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.78,Background,,0,0,0,,你再繼續吃下去真的會變成豬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.28,Background,,0,0,0,,不准說我是豬!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看到滿那個樣子後 更不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.54,Background,,0,0,0,,肥豬~肥豬~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.58,Background,,0,0,0,,閉嘴! 給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果搭檔殺手的傳聞真有其事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再和她搭檔兩次 你就可能會喪命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有和Zero Two搭檔 我才能找回所謂的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經 做好覺悟了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也不會阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莓?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我身為隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也得做出相應的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,覺悟...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 叫龍應該要全數殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都不該是妳違背命令的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那點程度的叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒有必要做到如此過火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為此 我們還差點損失一名操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,妳有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好想快點離開這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真讓人喘不過氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我說妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只要Darling還活著就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,反正其他傢伙全滅也是遲早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然所屬單位不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但你們是同為FRANXX操縱者的夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,夥伴? 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多少個 弱者都只會礙事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還只是非正規部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1064,980)}Irregular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1501,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但他們仍是從高適性樣本中揀選出的操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妳會有那種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因為妳的存在很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你想說 因為我不是人類?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我僅就能力方面而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(801.6,980)}廣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1098.4,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 讓016操縱鶴望蘭的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是等不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才本部下達了指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要請妳回到前線去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果搭檔殺手的傳聞真有其事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再和她搭檔兩次 你就可能會喪命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 操縱到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 要置我於死地般...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,當時還帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她當時在笑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,廣那傢伙 又在一個人訓練了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沒人阻止 他大概會永遠跑下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,廣他啊 個性意外地認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和我對他的印象截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是說 他還沒放棄和那女的搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1137.333,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,以現況來看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是廣唯一能繼續待在這的方法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可是這不就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是Zero Two離開這 那傢伙也得跟著離開吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或許 讓廣隨著Zero Two去對他來說比較好...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一個人下去 太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊 妳是不是忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那女的身上可是流著叫龍的血耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她可不是人類哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,滿傷成那樣妳也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,廣是在明白這一切後 仍然想和她搭檔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,莓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且真要講邁向死亡 我們不也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,憑我們的表現 再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候戰死都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有鶴望蘭相助便無法打倒叫龍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(657.333,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等著我們的 只有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再重踏覆轍以往的失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要說失敗的話 妳也有責任不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 所以不會再有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望大家能齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都是小隊的一份子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小隊嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我知道啦 那點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那番話 很有隊長的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 也差不多是向爸爸們展現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們優秀的一面的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.58,Background,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 或許我們也能夠...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,生野妳也是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 滿一定也不會再讓自己失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,以搭檔的身分好好支持著他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,本都市 為了與第26都市進行連通作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1379.2,980)}Kissing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,即將轉換成移動型態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,重述
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,本都市 為了與第26都市進行連通作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1379.2,980)}Kissing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,即將轉換成移動型態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我幹嘛躲起來啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩兩次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我就會...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,原來在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等!? 為什麼妳會...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,靠 靠太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一起離開這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,別管那群弱小的傢伙們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要有Darling就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你 才能是我的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也和其他人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,認為我是怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,叫龍!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,發現蟲型叫龍一架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(858,980)}Worm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝著第13要塞都市潛行移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,推斷是被都市轉換形態時的能源反應所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我還能...我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,走得動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這點小傷 不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我扶你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...都是我太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,叫龍的種類仍然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然目前只觀測到一架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不排除其他個體仍潛伏中的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,別掉以輕心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,各機體 開始連結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這次請妳可別再出問題了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡開始擋住牠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,敵方只有一架嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,目前看起來是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就算先換好服裝鶴望蘭也無法出動的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(993.333,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒說唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,解決了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不 手感不對 應該沒有破壞到核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不先找出核就打不倒牠對吧 那快點...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還有另一架嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,得去救他們才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再撐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,地面突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就說了應該讓我們去才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呿 小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那台剛降落在這的運輸機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,上面載了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,CODE:002 請跟我們走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是來迎接妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,請妳老老實實地配合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two 妳將會重返前線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...當然是一個人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,回 回去是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,動作快 趁FRANXX吸引叫龍的注意力時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two 這到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling 好像到此為止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是和Darling的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或許就不會迎來這樣的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本是如此認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真想和你在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我們得在此訣別了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這是爸爸們下的決定...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,關於Zero Two「搭檔殺手」的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,往後仍必須為了爸爸們在第一線奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,特別的雌式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1060.8,980)}Pistil
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,於此同時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,作為其搭檔的雄式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1162.667,980)}Stamens
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自然得承受其相對強度的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你得記住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她和你們這群普通的孩子完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的意思是 她不是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,直截了當地說就是如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你即使看見我的角也不會畏懼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你也和其他人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,認為我是怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真想和你在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不...Zero Two和我都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 廣!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說 其實我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕 害怕著和妳搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想必 此刻的我仍然會覺得恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那跟妳不是人類無關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而是我始終沒有做好那份覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次見到妳時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就覺得妳十分地動人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自信洋溢 無所畏懼的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,即使傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,仍挺身對抗叫龍的妳 令我覺得美麗無比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也讓一直裹足不前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,「如果和妳一起的話 是否就能飛上天空?」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有了這樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我總算察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想的...不是單純操縱FRANXX而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要 成為妳的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 拜託妳不要走 Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這下想回去也回不去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,被那樣說了一堆害臊的話 還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想和我一起操縱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,完整地說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我一起操縱鶴望蘭吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1114,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣才像是 我的Darling嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要衝刺囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他們往大門方向跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 現在立刻下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和Darling出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有許可你們是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎 Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的能啟動嗎 憑我這樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的 如果是我和Darling的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和Zero Two一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好 振翅高飛吧 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在...操縱著FRANXX
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 這就是Darling的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,像是自己在妳的意識中漫延開來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,區分彼此存在的界線漸漸難以分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 卻一點都不難受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有相同的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們真的很合得來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過厲害的可不只有這樣而已喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(949.333,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是廣嗎...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行! 這次再依靠鶴望蘭的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1114.667,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟大家一樣 都是小隊的一份子...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 廣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊交給你負責
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們集中對付眼前這架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,手感不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,核到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,見鬼了...居然是連在一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這種長度 要找出核也太難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,說歸說還是得找出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,吼 誰想個辦法讓牠不要動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是說 動是不會動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,現在要怎麼辦啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,廣...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,廣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,叫龍確認擊破 各機體 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(892,980)}賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,無視爸爸們的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子難道一開始就...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣一來 局勢又變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,CODE:016和鶴望蘭的適性值已然證實的此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(802.667,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(623.5,980)}賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸們會採取怎樣的行動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,夢想著能飛上藍天的那天到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也曾經認為那是癡人說夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而一度放棄過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但如今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我總算尋獲了翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,即使...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那同時是以我的性命作為代價的雙面刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少最後...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我還能夠再翱翔一次
